  "title": "Erythema ab igne",
  "body_html": "Erythema ab igne is a skin disorder caused by over exposure to infrared radiation. Characteristic features include reticulated, erythematous patches with hyperpigmentation and telangiectasia. A typical history would be an elderly women who always sits next to an open fire.<br /><br />If the cause is not treated then patients may go on to develop squamous cell skin cancer.<br /><br /><CENTER><table><tr><td align = 'left' colspan='2'><img class='ajaximage' src = 'https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_MRCEMnotes/ddx007.jpg' /></td></tr><tr><td valign='top' align='left'> <span style = 'font-size:11px; color:LightGray;'>&copy; Image used on license from </span><a href='http://www.dermnet.org.nz'  target='_blank' style = 'font-size:11px; color:LightGray;' >DermNet NZ</a></td><td align='right'></td></tr></table></CENTER><div class='imagetext'>Erythema ab igne</div><br /><CENTER><table><tr><td align = 'left' colspan='2'><a data-fancybox class='fancybox' rel='group' href='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_MRCEMnotes/ddd008b.jpg'><img class='ajaximage' src='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_MRCEMnotes/ddd008.jpg'/></a></td></tr><tr><td valign='top' align='left'> <span style = 'font-size:11px; color:LightGray;'>&copy; Image used on license from </span><a href='http://www.dermnet.org.nz'  target='_blank' style = 'font-size:11px; color:LightGray;' >DermNet NZ</a></td><td align='right'><a data-fancybox class='fancybox lbmagglasslink' rel='group' href='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_MRCEMnotes/ddd008b.jpg'><img src='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/css/images/mag_glass.png'/></a></td></tr></table></CENTER><div class='imagetext'>Erythema ab igne</div></div>\n\n<div id=\"mybodylinks\"></div>\n\n<div id=\"mybodymedia\"></div>\n\n\n<div id=\"categorynum\">5</div>\n\n<div id=\"subcategorynum\">3625</div>\n\n<div id=\"categoryname\">Pathology</div>\n\n<div id=\"subcategoryname\">Dermatology</div>\n<div id=\"mybody\">\n\n<div id=\"body_content\">\nErythema ab igne is a skin disorder caused by over exposure to infrared radiation. Characteristic features include reticulated, erythematous patches with hyperpigmentation and telangiectasia. A typical history would be an elderly women who always sits next to an open fire.<br /><br />If the cause is not treated then patients may go on to develop squamous cell skin cancer.<br /><br /><CENTER><table><tr><td align = 'left' colspan='2'><img class='ajaximage' src = 'https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_MRCEMnotes/ddx007.jpg' /></td></tr><tr><td valign='top' align='left'> <span style = 'font-size:11px; color:LightGray;'>&copy; Image used on license from </span><a href='http://www.dermnet.org.nz'  target='_blank' style = 'font-size:11px; color:LightGray;' >DermNet NZ</a></td><td align='right'></td></tr></table></CENTER><div class='imagetext'>Erythema ab igne</div><br /><CENTER><table><tr><td align = 'left' colspan='2'><a data-fancybox class='fancybox' rel='group' href='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_MRCEMnotes/ddd008b.jpg'><img class='ajaximage' src='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_MRCEMnotes/ddd008.jpg'/></a></td></tr><tr><td valign='top' align='left'> <span style = 'font-size:11px; color:LightGray;'>&copy; Image used on license from </span><a href='http://www.dermnet.org.nz'  target='_blank' style = 'font-size:11px; color:LightGray;' >DermNet NZ</a></td><td align='right'><a data-fancybox class='fancybox lbmagglasslink' rel='group' href='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_MRCEMnotes/ddd008b.jpg'><img src='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/css/images/mag_glass.png'/></a></td></tr></table></CENTER><div class='imagetext'>Erythema ab igne</div></div>\n\n\n<BR><BR><br><br>",
